# Interactive Shopping List

This project is a simple interactive shopping list application that allows users to add items, mark them as purchased, and clear the list. It demonstrates basic array manipulation, DOM manipulation, and event handling using JavaScript.

## Features

- Add items to the shopping list.
- Mark items as purchased by clicking on them.
- Clear the entire list.
- Edit existing list items.
- Persist the list using local storage.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Getting Started

To get a local copy up and running follow these simple steps.

### Prerequisites

You will need a web browser to run the application.

